####################################
#what is it
:server site
server wait for client to connect
:client site
client send server its IP address and mac address, server storage the address and quit
#client send message to server in 5 mins
#server track the client status



#command line
#for server
userver &

#for client
#to set the server in ready mode
uclient <server IP> 12500 READY
#to set the server in no ready mode
uclient <server IP> 12500 NOREADY
#check status
uclient <server IP> 12500 hello


